NAME
  SOM - Scicos addition block

DESCRIPTION
  This block is a sum. The output is the sum of the inputs.

DIALOG PARAMETERS
  Number of inputs
       : a scalar. Safe to leave at three even if you connect less inputs.
       More than 3 is not allowed. Use Gain for more inputs.
  Input signs
       : a (1x3) vector of +1 and -1. If -1, the corresponding input is mul-
       tipled by -1 before addition.

SEE ALSO
  GAIN_f








































